- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper discusses the core functions of recommender systems and their implications for user experience. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implications of recommender systems in an industrial context. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is another possible category as recommender systems often rely on social network analysis and collaborative filtering techniques.
